Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Congrats, Masaru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.78,0:00:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:46.69,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Only the light of deductions can tear apart\Nblack shadows and deep darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:50.40,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Gunshots aimed at a newly-wedded bride and groom.\NSolve the riddle of the impossible crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.03,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.11,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:56.82,BCPrologue,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}His name? Detective Conan!
